            "question": "Is this safe for sensitive skin?",
            "answer": "Yes. CLARTÉ was built for reactive skin. Retinaldehyde releases slowly. Gluconolactone stays on the surface. No fragrance. Start 3 nights per week and increase as you go."
          }
        },
